Tiny-RedBayes version 0.01
==========================

Perform naive Bayesian classification using an array of words per category and Redis as a storage backend

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

   Redis
   Try::Tiny

